      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        140.41,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0020",
      "text": "The Payload of the request contains, among other parameters, the Alias_ID to be deacti-",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        406.96,
        539.92,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0021",
      "text": "vated by the Nx_Port.  The format of the Payload is shown in table 87.The Nx_Port shall transmit a",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        539.82,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0022",
      "text": "LS_ACC to notify the Alias Server of a deactivation of an Alias_ID.  ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        394.78,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0023",
      "text": "Alias Group Identifier (Alias_ID):",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        250.23,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0024",
      "text": " The Alias Group Identifier field shall contain the Alias_ID that the",
      "bbox": [
        250.26,
        550.96,
        540.01,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0025",
      "text": "Nx_Port no longer recognizes.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        230.45,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0026",
      "text": "4.2.30.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        214.86,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0027",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        138.19,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0028",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies the rejection of the NDACT Request.  An LS_RJT shall be returned if the",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        610.96,
        539.99,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0029",
      "text": "Alias_ID is unable to be deactivated as an Alias_ID.  A reason code of \"Unable to perform command",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        540.07,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p106_s0030",
      "text": "request\" shall be generated, along with one of the reason code explanations in table 147.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
